objects.name: event
objects.title: Waking Up
objects.text: You wake up on the side of the road. Behind you a destroyed city and barricades. You have to reach the ship in the North!

objects.name: event
objects.title: Gather
objects.text: There are some trees growing here. You should look around them for useful things and pick everything up. Watch your stats - hunger and thirst are a constant threat in this broken world.

objects.name: event
objects.title: Almanac
objects.text:
The Almanac provides details about all items.

Just right-click item slots and crafting buttons.

objects.name: event
objects.title: Zombies!
objects.text: The road in front of you is blocked. Two unfortunates "survived" this accident, and now walk around as undead. They are really dangerous  better head on and deal with them later.

objects.name: event
objects.title: Zombie 101
objects.text: Try to lure Zeds towards you. Attacking them will cause others in the area join the fight. When you walk right into them, they  will attack you first.

objects.name: event
objects.title: Be prepared
objects.text: Any weapon is better than no weapon. Check your inventory. Sharp sticks, tools or stones are good  true weapons are better. Check item properties in the Almanac.

objects.name: event
objects.title: A companion!
objects.text: A small dog is bravely facing one of these monsters! He looks like he could be a little down.

objects.name: event
objects.title: You found it!
objects.text: After all the hardships you made it to the ship in time! You take your beloved in your arms and together you look over the devastated land while the ship is heading towards a hopefully safe future.

objects.name: event
objects.title: The Horde!
objects.text: You see a huge horde of Zombies slowly shambling across the street. At this speed it will take days before they are gone. You better turn around and search for an alternative route!

objects.name: event
objects.title: Locked
objects.text: The content of the crate should make your tutorial run easier, but it is locked. Equip the axe to break it.
